[PC setup]

1. Download and Install Ubuntu on PC
 -> https://releases.ubuntu.com/16.04.7/ubuntu-16.04.7-desktop-amd64.iso
 -> https://releases.ubuntu.com/16.04.7/ubuntu-16.04.6-desktop-i386.iso

2. Download Win32DiskImager
 -> https://sourceforge.net/projects/win32diskimager/files/latest/download

3. Image Write

4. RemotePC booting setup : USB booting (F12)

5. Install Ubuntu 16.04
 -> https://ubuntu.com/tutorials/install-ubuntu-desktop#1-overview
 
6. hangul setup
 -> t : sudo apt-get update
 -> t : sudo apt-get install ibus ibus-hangul
 -> language support : 한국어 / ibus 설정
 -> keyboard : typing 에서 Ctrl+space
 -> text entry : Korean(hangul)(IBUS) 추가하고 스위칭은 Crtl+space


[SBC setup]

1. Download and Install Raspbian on ROBOT
 -> http://www.robotis.com/service/download.php?no=1738

2. Download BalenaEtcher
 -> https://www.balena.io/etcher/

3. Image Write

4. Install Raspbian for Turtlebot



[ trouble shooting ]

1. reboot 이나 poweroff 시 오작동 문제 : sudo gedit /etc/default/grub
 -> https://forum.ubuntu-kr.org/viewtopic.php?t=10134
 -> https://ghostweb.tistory.com/824

2. Raspberry PI 에 OpenCR 펌웨어 설치시 업그레이드 꼭 진행 :sudo apt-get upgrade


